quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  42,13,"Ibyo yabategetse mu idini ni na byo yategetse Nuhu, ndetse n’ibyo twaguhishuriye (yewe Muhamadi), ni na byo twategetse Ibrahimu, Musa na Issa, tuvuga ko mugomba gutunganya idini mwirinda kunyuranya na ryo. Ababangikanyamana baremererwa n’ibyo mubahamagarira (byo kugaragira Imana imwe). Allah yihitiramo uwo ashaka, akanayobora inzira ye uwicuza"
  42,14,"Kandi (abayoboke b’Intumwa za mbere) batandukanye nyuma yo kugerwaho n’ubumenyi (Qur’an) bitewe no kugirirana ishyari n’inzangano. N’iyo bitaza kuba ijambo ryaturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe ryabanje ryo (kudahaniraho) kugeza igihe kizwi (imperuka), bari gucirwaho iteka (ryo kurimbuka). Mu by’ukuri ba bandi bahaweho igitabo (Tawurati na Injili) umurage nyuma y’abo (bahakanyi), bagishidikanyaho mu buryo buteye amakenga"
  42,15,"Bityo, iryo (dini ry’Ubuyisilamu ry’Intumwa zose) ube ari ryo uhamagarira (abantu), kandi ukomeze utungane nk’uko wabitegetswe, ntuzanakurikire irari ryabo. Unavuge uti “Nemera ibyo Allah yahishuye mu bitabo (byahawe Intumwa), kandi nategetswe gukoresha ubutabera muri mwe. Allah ni We Nyagasani wacu akaba ari na we Nyagasani wanyu. Dufite ibikorwa byacu namwe mukagira ibyanyu. Nta mpaka zikwiye kuba hagati yacu namwe. Allah azaduhuriza hamwe twese (aducire imanza). Kandi iwe ni ho garukiro (ryacu twese)"
  42,16,"Na ba bandi bajya impaka ku idini rya Allah nyuma y’uko riyobotswe, impaka zabo nta shingiro zifite kwa Nyagasani wabo. Bazagerwaho n’uburakari (bwa Allah), kandi bazahanishwa ibihano bikaze"
  42,17,Allah ni We wahishuye igitabo gikubiyemo ukuri n’ubutabera. Ese ni iki cyakubwira ko imperuka itari hafi
  42,18,"Ariko abatayemera bifuza ko yakwihutishwa, naho ba bandi bayemera barayitinya kandi bazi neza ko ari ukuri. Mumenye ko mu by’ukuri abajya impaka ku mperuka bari mu buyobe bwa kure"
  42,19,"Allah agenza buhoro abagaragu be, aha amafunguro uwo ashaka kandi ni Umunyembaraga, Nyiricyubahiro bihebuje"
  42,20,"Ugamije gushaka ibihembo by’umunsi w’imperuka, tuzamwongerera ibihembo bye, n’ugamije gushaka ibihembo by’isi, tuzamuhaho ariko ku munsi w’imperuka nta mugabane azagira"
  42,21,"Ese (abahakanyi) baba bafite ibigirwamana byabashyiriyeho amategeko mu idini Allah atigeze abahera uburenganzira? N’iyo bitaza kuba ijambo ryo kudahaniraho, bari gucirwaho iteka (ryo kurimbuka). Kandi mu by’ukuri abahakanyi bazahanishwa ibihano bibabaza"
  42,22,"(Ku munsi w’imperuka) uzabona abahakanyi batewe ubwoba (n’ibihano) by’ibyo bakoze, kandi bigomba kubageraho nta kabuza. Nyamara ba bandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, bazaba bari mu busitani bwo mu ijuru, bahabwa ibyo bashaka kwa Nyagasani wabo. Izo ni zo ngabire z’ikirenga"
  42,23,"Iyo ni yo nkuru nziza Allah aha abagaragu be bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza. Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “(Kubagezaho ubutumwa) simbibasabira igihembo (yemwe bantu b’i Maka), usibye gusa urukundo rw’isano (mfitanye namwe). Kandi uzakora icyiza, tuzamutuburira ibihembo byacyo. Mu by’ukuri Allah ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Ushima bihebuje (ibikorwa by’abagaragu be).”"
  42,24,"Bavuga ko (Muhamadi) yahimbiye Allah ikinyoma, ariko iyo Allah aza kubishaka yari kudanangira umutima wawe (iyo uramuka ubikoze). Kandi Allah akuraho ibitari ukuri agashimangiza ukuri amagambo ye. Mu by’ukuri We ni Umumenyi uhebuje w’ibiri mu bituza (by’abantu)"
  42,25,"Ni na We wakira ukwicuza kw’abagaragu be, akanababarira ibibi. Kandi azi neza ibyo mukora"
  42,26,"Yakira ubusabe bwa ba bandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, ndetse akanabongerera mu ngabire ze. Kandi abahakanyi bazahanishwa ibihano bikaze"